%% CURRENT architecture — matches CLAUDE.md "Architecture" section.
%% No separate backend exists. See "flowchart LR.mmd" for the future
%% Express.js-integration plan (TES-58, Backlog, not started).
flowchart LR
  User[User browser] --> Next[Next.js 16 App Router<br/>React 19]
  Next --> Clerk[Clerk auth<br/>identity + session]

  Next --> Proxy[proxy.ts<br/>Clerk middleware<br/>protects all routes except sign-in/sign-up]
  Proxy --> Server[Server Component / Route Handler<br/>app/lib/data/*.ts]

  Server --> SupaClient[lib/supabase/server.ts<br/>createSupabaseServerClient<br/>attaches Clerk JWT template 'supabase' as bearer, anon key]
  SupaClient --> RLS{Supabase RLS<br/>app_private.* helper functions<br/>security boundary}

  RLS --> DB[(Supabase Postgres)]
  RLS --> Storage[(Supabase Storage<br/>compliance-evidence bucket<br/>tenant-UUID path prefix)]

  DB --> Server
  Storage --> Server
  Server --> Next
